'''宝拉·米歇尔·怀特-凯恩'''（{{lang-en|Paula Michelle White-Cain}}，{{bd|1966年|04月20日}}）是美国的传道人、作家、{{tsl|en|televangelist|电视传道者}}、[[成功神学|成功神学]]倡导者。

怀特是[[唐纳德·特朗普|唐纳德·特朗普]]政府的福音派顾问委员会（Evangelical Advisory Board）主席。<ref name="WashPost">{{cite news|last=Zauzmer|first=Julie|date=2016-12-29|title=Paula White, prosperity preacher once investigated by Senate, is a controversial pick for inauguration|newspaper=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/acts-of-faith/wp/2016/12/29/paula-white-prosperity-preacher-once-investigated-by-senate-is-a-controversial-pick-for-inauguration-prayer/|accessdate=2016-12-30|archive-date=2018-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181201105549/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/acts-of-faith/wp/2016/12/29/paula-white-prosperity-preacher-once-investigated-by-senate-is-a-controversial-pick-for-inauguration-prayer/|dead-url=no}}</ref>她在2017年1月20日[[2017年美國總統就職典禮|特朗普的就職典禮]]期间{{tsl|en|invocation|祝祷}}，<ref>{{cite web|date=2017-01-19|title=Who's who in the inauguration ceremonies|url=http://www.foxnews.com/politics/slideshow/2017/01/19/whos-who-in-inauguration-ceremonies.html#/slide/pastor-paula-white|work=[[Fox_News|Fox News]]|access-date=2020-11-05|archive-date=2018-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180817161203/http://www.foxnews.com/politics/slideshow/2017/01/19/whos-who-in-inauguration-ceremonies.html#/slide/pastor-paula-white|dead-url=no}}</ref>是首名为总统祝祷的女性神职人员。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/19/us/trumps-pastor-paula-white.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-11-05 |archive-date=2020-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114040358/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/19/us/trumps-pastor-paula-white.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>2019年11月，特朗普任命她为白宫{{tsl|en|Office of Public Liaison|公众联络办公室}}{{tsl|en|Center for Faith and Opportunity Initiatives|信仰与机遇倡议中心}}的特别顾问。<ref>{{cite web|last=Perry|first=Douglas|date=2019-11-04|title=Paula White, Donald Trump's new adviser, ratchets up rhetoric, denounces 'demonic' networks opposing president's 'calling'|url=https://www.oregonlive.com/politics/2019/11/paula-white-do